Reviews: Love my 9 inch and 12 inch tongs.
long ones ideal for the BBQ
These stylish little tongs are durable to cook with and sleek enough to have on the table for service.A long and a short one in the purchase they are great!
Handy to have a long and a shorter version.  The pull close/open is quick & easy to use.
Exactly what I'd hope for.  Has a pull out ring for locking/unlocking.
Perfect

I was a bit sceptical after reading some of the reviews, but after 4 months of using and abusing them, washing them exclusively in the dishwasher, they still look like new.Let's be honest, they're just tongs, but they feel nice and quality built.
Great items for great price. Couldn't find anything in general shops for the same quality and price tag
Quality of product excellent
Good quality thongs!
